Check EC2 CPU, Memory, Disk, and Network utilization using CloudWatch Metrics.

Investigate spikes in resource usage (e.g., CPU > 80% for 5 mins).

Verify that CloudWatch Alarms are working correctly (e.g., Low Disk Space).

Action: If an instance shows high CPU for a long time, consider scaling or troubleshooting.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Common Alarms to Monitor:

EC2 CPU Utilization > 80%

EBS Volume Usage > 90%

Application Latency > 500ms

RDS Free Storage < 20%
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
